@node History
 V1.1 - Initial release.
 V1.2 - 1) Added software reboots detection.
        2) Fixed a stupid bug with error code in case of invalid arguments
        given.
        3) Added error message printing in case of errors.
        4) Added a patch for ColdReboot() function in v39.
 V1.3 - 1) "System failure detected" message is now written before "System
        started" message to make a logfile more readable.
        2) Fixed a FidoNet address and changed E-Mail address in the
        documentation. Thanks to John Jshmetov (2:5090/65.255@FidoNet).
 V1.4 - Fixed a stupid bug, which caused startup time to be equal to last
        shutdown time.
@endnode
